#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "**End of stay**"
msgstr "**Einde verblijf**"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "Discharge or death documents"
msgstr "Ontslag- of overlijdensdocumenten"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "**eAgreement**"
msgstr "**eAgreement**"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "MR/MRS agreements (care convention)"
msgstr "MR/MRS-akkoorden (zorgovereenkomst)"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "**OA**"
msgstr "**OA**"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "Statements and letters from the insurance body"
msgstr "Afrekeningen en brieven van de verzekeringsinstelling"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "**Convention**"
msgstr "**Conventie**"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "Convention"
msgstr "Conventie"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "**Medical form**"
msgstr "**Medisch formulier**"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "Medical forms and certificates"
msgstr "Medische formulieren en attesten"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "**Billing**"
msgstr "**Facturatie**"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "Statements and invoices"
msgstr "Afrekeningen en facturen"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "**CPAS**"
msgstr "**OCMW**"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "CPAS coverage"
msgstr "OCMW-tenlasteneming"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "**GDPR**"
msgstr "**GDPR**"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:92
msgid "GDPR consents and documents"
msgstr "GDPR-toestemmingen en -documenten"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:121
msgid "Start light"
msgstr "Begin licht"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:124
msgid ""
"The **Default tags** are **optional**. Leave the field **empty** to start, "
"or put a single generic tag in it: you can always tag each document more "
"precisely afterwards in the Documents app."
msgstr ""
"De **standaardlabels** zijn **optioneel**. Laat het veld **leeg** om te "
"beginnen, of zet er één generiek label in: u kunt elk document nadien altijd"
" nauwkeuriger labelen in de toepassing Documenten."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:129
msgid "Who can see the documents"
msgstr "Wie de documenten kan zien"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:131
msgid ""
"Centralized documents **inherit the rights of the resident's folder**: only "
"users with access to the **Documents** app can view them. They have no "
"individual owner, which prevents a file from \"belonging\" to a single staff"
" member and keeps the whole resident folder consistent and manageable by the"
" team."
msgstr ""
"Gecentraliseerde documenten **erven de rechten van de map van de bewoner**: "
"alleen gebruikers met toegang tot de toepassing **Documenten** kunnen ze "
"raadplegen. Ze hebben geen individuele eigenaar, wat voorkomt dat een "
"bestand aan één personeelslid « toebehoort » en de hele bewonersmap coherent"
" en beheersbaar door het team houdt."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:136
msgid "Segregated by facility"
msgstr "Gescheiden per instelling"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:139
msgid ""
"In multi-company, **each facility has its own \"Residents\" root folder** "
"and its own centralization configuration. A resident's documents therefore "
"stay segregated within their company."
msgstr ""
"In multi-company heeft **elke instelling haar eigen hoofdmap « Bewoners »** "
"en haar eigen centralisatieconfiguratie. De documenten van een bewoner "
"blijven dus gescheiden binnen hun bedrijf."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:144
msgid "Enabling or disabling"
msgstr "In- of uitschakelen"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:146
msgid ""
"Centralization is **enabled by default**. You control it with the **Nursing "
"home** block in **Settings > Documents > File centralization**:"
msgstr ""
"De centralisatie is **standaard ingeschakeld**. U regelt ze met het blok "
"**Woonzorgcentrum** in **Instellingen > Documenten > Centralisatie van "
"bestanden**:"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:149
msgid "**checking** the block **enables** automatic filing;"
msgstr "het blok **aanvinken** **schakelt** de automatische klassering in;"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:150
msgid ""
"**unchecking** the block **stops** centralization of **future** attachments "
"— documents already filed **stay in place**, nothing is deleted or moved."
msgstr ""
"het blok **uitvinken** **stopt** de centralisatie van **toekomstige** "
"bijlagen — reeds geklasseerde documenten **blijven staan**, er wordt niets "
"verwijderd of verplaatst."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:153
msgid ""
"The details of the three settings (activation, **root folder**, **default "
"tags**) are described on the [Document settings](../configuration/reglages-"
"documents.md) page."
msgstr ""
"De details van de drie instellingen (activering, **hoofdmap**, "
"**standaardlabels**) worden beschreven op de pagina [Instellingen "
"Documenten](../configuration/reglages-documents.md)."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:156
msgid "Key takeaways"
msgstr "Om te onthouden"

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:158
msgid ""
"Every attachment added to a resident's **message thread** or **record** is "
"**automatically copied** into their Documents folder."
msgstr ""
"Elke bijlage die aan de **berichtendraad** of de **fiche** van een bewoner "
"wordt toegevoegd, wordt **automatisch gekopieerd** naar zijn map Documenten."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:160
msgid ""
"Filing concerns **residents only** — not contacts, vendors or employees."
msgstr ""
"De klassering betreft **alleen bewoners** — niet de contacten, leveranciers "
"of werknemers."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:161
msgid ""
"The facility's **default tags** are **applied automatically** to every "
"centralized document."
msgstr ""
"De **standaardlabels** van de instelling worden **automatisch toegepast** op"
" elk gecentraliseerd document."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:163
msgid ""
"The resident's **personal folder** (and its subfolders) is created "
"automatically; the **Documents** button on the record opens it directly."
msgstr ""
"De **persoonlijke map** van de bewoner (en zijn submappen) wordt automatisch"
" aangemaakt; de knop **Documenten** op de fiche opent ze rechtstreeks."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:165
msgid ""
"Centralization is **enabled by default** and is disabled by unchecking the "
"**Nursing home** block — documents already filed stay in place."
msgstr ""
"De centralisatie is **standaard ingeschakeld** en wordt uitgeschakeld door "
"het blok **Woonzorgcentrum** uit te vinken — reeds geklasseerde documenten "
"blijven staan."

#: ../../content/documents/centralisation.md:167
msgid "The setting and root folder are **specific to each facility**."
msgstr "De instelling en de hoofdmap zijn **specifiek voor elke instelling**."

